  "name": "Pyro Hypostasis",
  "desc": "Code Name: Ayin. A high-purity Pyro entity.<br/>According to researchers, Elemental Hypostases are related to anomalies in local Elemental veins. But whether it is the existence of Elemental Hypostases that have affected Elemental veins or the mutated Elemental Energy that created Elemental Hypostases remains to be confirmed.",
