              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "Protects itself with a cubical shell that is elementally inert. Has two states: Ignited and Extinguished. In the Ignited state, the Pyro Hypostasis's core is not exposed and it continuously regenerates HP. Only after <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">Extinguishing it with the right elemental reactions</span> will you have an opportunity to strike. In the Extinguished state, the Pyro Hypostasis will generate Fire Seeds in an attempt to re-ignite."
                ]
